    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Descend into forgotten memories. Uncover the truth buried beneath silence</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a man with no past, only fragments. Once a child in an experimental orphanage hidden behind Cold War iron walls, now lost in a Black Forest where memories hunt you like shadows. Voices speak. The world bends. Every step deeper reveals pieces of the boy you once were... and the weapon they tried to create.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/7ecde74116c0fe991aef475d59923041.poster.avif?t=1746728661\" width=608 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/7ecde74116c0fe991aef475d59923041.webm?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/7ecde74116c0fe991aef475d59923041.mp4?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHYCHOLOGICAL HORROR GAME WITH RICH STORY AND STRONG VISUALS</h2>Immerse yourself in a psychological horror where your past is a puzzle, and your mind is both weapon and prison. Unravel a haunting story set in a decaying world, filled with twisted memories and dangerous choices, where nightmare and reality blur.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/ce51416c4220c6522ac57cc2395c334d.poster.avif?t=1746728661\" width=608 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/ce51416c4220c6522ac57cc2395c334d.webm?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/ce51416c4220c6522ac57cc2395c334d.mp4?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Safe Stealth</h2>Move carefully through the shadows, using your wits and the environment to stay unseen. Rely on your stealth skills.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/00380989960611418e9c265709290eed.poster.avif?t=1746728661\" width=608 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/00380989960611418e9c265709290eed.webm?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/00380989960611418e9c265709290eed.mp4?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And GO AGGRESSIVE</h2>When you're pushed to the edge, transform into your darker self, unleashing violence and chaos to take down enemies head-on. Sometimes, brute force is the only way forward.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/b648d13cd60f2e5f7337f7fc6800c367.poster.avif?t=1746728661\" width=608 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/b648d13cd60f2e5f7337f7fc6800c367.webm?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/b648d13cd60f2e5f7337f7fc6800c367.mp4?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Keeps You Alive</h2>Managing your resources is crucial for survival. Your inventory holds a variety of tools and weapons. Choose wisely.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/41df994825563798914db402481083eb.poster.avif?t=1746728661\" width=608 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/41df994825563798914db402481083eb.webm?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257690/extras/41df994825563798914db402481083eb.mp4?t=1746728661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EMBRACE A FULL-ACTION HORROR EXPERIENCE</h2><br>Some of the Key Features are: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced IK<br></li><li>Physical animations<br></li><li>Dismemberment system<br></li><li>Destructible environment and more</li></ul>",
